05-進階紅綠燈 - 機器人學入門




 








機器人學入門搜尋這個協作平臺












課程綱要105學年資訊科機器人專題製作進度課程導引Arduino自學Processing資料三創課程大綱其他基礎練習01-入門02-七彩閃爍燈03-情境燈製作04-紅綠燈製作05-進階紅綠燈06-按鈕開關07-光感測器08-小夜燈10-光控紅綠燈感應器判斷超音波感應器實驗室簡介愛學網註冊方式技術資料大量藍芽模組設定教具相關開放課程網際網路應用藍芽房屋監控資優營課程綱要105資優營筆記液晶顯示+超音波紅綠燈課程回顧與重點整理遙控車Arduino入門可調燈按鍵切換LED燈柔和小夜燈自走車協作平臺地圖
相關連結滿意度調查表網路世界須知網路中心



 

基礎練習‎ > ‎
  

05-進階紅綠燈



學習重點：能瞭解陣列的意義。能用一維陣列撰寫程式。使用程式：範例   -->  05.control --> Arrarysint timer = 100;           // The higher the number, the slower the timing.int ledPins[] = {  2, 7, 4, 6, 5, 3};       // an array of pin numbers to which LEDs are attachedint pinCount = 6;           // the number of pins (i.e. the length of the array)void setup() {  // the array elements are numbered from 0 to (pinCount - 1).  // use a for loop to initialize each pin as an output:  for (int thisPin = 0; thisPin < pinCount; thisPin++) {    pinMode(ledPins[thisPin], OUTPUT);  }}void loop() {  // loop from the lowest pin to the highest:  for (int thisPin = 0; thisPin < pinCount; thisPin++) {    // turn the pin on:    digitalWrite(ledPins[thisPin], HIGH);    delay(timer);    // turn the pin off:    digitalWrite(ledPins[thisPin], LOW);  }  // loop from the highest pin to the lowest:  for (int thisPin = pinCount - 1; thisPin >= 0; thisPin--) {    // turn the pin on:    digitalWrite(ledPins[thisPin], HIGH);    delay(timer);    // turn the pin off:    digitalWrite(ledPins[thisPin], LOW);  }}說明：理解輸出的對應關係。修改上列程式，成為紅綠燈。int timer[] = {1000,300,2000,1000,300,2000};           // 每一個燈號亮燈時間.int ledPins[] = {8, 9,10 ,8, 9,10  };       // 亮燈順序int pinCount = 6;           // the number of pins (i.e. the length of the array)void setup() {  // the array elements are numbered from 0 to (pinCount - 1).  // use a for loop to initialize each pin as an output:  for (int thisPin = 0; thisPin < pinCount; thisPin++) {    pinMode(ledPins[thisPin], OUTPUT);  }}void loop() {  // loop from the lowest pin to the highest:  for (int thisPin = 0; thisPin < pinCount; thisPin++) {    // turn the pin on:    digitalWrite(ledPins[thisPin], HIGH);    delay(timer[thisPin]);    // turn the pin off:    digitalWrite(ledPins[thisPin], LOW);  } }參考資料：陣列說明1、說明2、



 



